✦ PROJECT STATEMENT ✦

Modwanz is an Android-based application designed to enhance functionality,
provide a modern user interface, and empower end-users with refined tools
and systems. Built under the package:

**com.modwanz.manager**

the project reflects a mindset of innovation and continuous development.

This license emphasizes openness, collaboration, and respect for original
creation while ensuring freedom for modification and distribution.

